(1, 'The correct method of nail beauty, teach you how to do manicure', 2, '<p>Nail polish is an important part of beauty. Always use bright nail polish.</p><p>Step 1: Nail polish</p><p>First, remove old nail polish. Use cotton wool dipped in nail polish remover and rub it from the bottom of the nail to the tip several times to completely remove it. Then use manicure tools to shape the nails. After that, soak your hands in soapy water to soften the outer skin. Then use a towel to carefully clean your fingers and finger gaps. If necessary, use cuticle scissors to remove the thorns and uneven dead skin at the root of the nail.</p><p>Apply nail polish to the base of the nails first. Apply oil or cream around the nails and the root. Apply a protective layer to the nails. Shake the nail polish as much as possible before applying it. The color inside is evenly matched.</p><p>The second step is to choose the color.</p><p>Nail polish colors include rose red, red, flesh color, bean paste color, silver, etc. The popular nail polish now is translucent pink and beige light-colored nail polish. You must buy a lot of nail polish to match the color of the clothes. You need to buy a few main colors and the original colors at hand. Use overlapping colors or color matching to match the nail polish to achieve the desired effect. Overlapping color matching light coating high color saturation bright color system and then coating full of pearl space color system can create another color effect. Color matching color matching fingertip front nail nail painting color matching; or ten finger nails left The two areas on the right are painted with two or more colors in alternating colors or coordinated colors.</p><p><br/></p><p>Paint the original color of the crescent part of the nail with the same color as the base color. Paint the crescent part with red or black for a bright contrast; or paint the white base with tender orange, goose yellow, light blue or pink and other colors. Dye the nails in the full crescent style.</p><p><br/></p><p>Step 3: Apply the nail polish carefully.</p><p><br/></p><p>Do not let the nail polish stick to the brush. Gently wipe the nail polish with the bottle mouth and adjust the brush bristles to be smooth. Pay attention to the following points when applying nail polish:</p><p><br/></p><p>Apply the nail polish by first applying the brush from the root of the nail to the front, then apply the brush along the edges of the nails. The brush is adjusted in order from the center to the sides. Brush evenly about three times to prevent nail polish from falling off quickly</p><p>To increase the durability of nail polish, first brush a layer on the front of the nail and then apply oil to the entire nail or apply oil in two batches: brush less oil in the first batch so that the oil can dry easily, and apply more oil in the second batch of nail polish. Use a cotton swab to clean the oil stains on the skin around the finger</p><p>The fourth step is to maintain nails</p><p>No matter what kind of nail polish is applied for a long time, the nails will not breathe and will easily turn yellow. Before applying nail polish, remove the nail polish and apply a layer of maintenance oil. It is recommended to use a transparent nail polish product to prevent pigment deposition</p><p>I believe that following the steps to do a manicure, you can customize it to satisfy yourself and let others be amazed by the manicure effect</p><p><br/></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, arial, 宋体, sans-serif, tahoma; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">指甲修饰乃性美容重要内容美总用鲜艳指甲油</span><br style=\"content: &quot;&quot;; display: block; height: 0px; margin: 15px 0px; width: 705px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, arial, 宋体, sans-serif, tahoma; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(2