tion: underline; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\"></span></strong></span></h2><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1. </span></strong><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">果凍膠黏貼</span></strong><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">穿戴甲使用方式</span></strong><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">Step1<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">：使用磨甲工具均勻打磨甲面，有助於增加穿戴甲與指甲的接觸面積，進而延長美甲的持久性。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">Step2<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">：利用酒精輕輕擦拭清潔甲面，以去除表面灰塵及油脂。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">Step3<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">：使用果凍膠黏貼在指甲，並以</span>45<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">度角將甲片附著在甲面。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">Step4<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">：按壓甲片約</span>30<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">秒，將其牢固地黏於指甲後便完成。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">果凍膠黏貼</span></strong><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">卸除方法</span></strong><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">果凍膠黏貼</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">卸除方式非常簡單，只需使用櫸木棒的斜口端插入於穿戴甲與原生甲的空隙處，並慢慢推移出果凍膠，同時也可利用木棒將甲片上的殘膠捲除，以供日後再次重複使用。</span></span></p><h2 style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;;\">2. </span></strong><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">固太膠黏貼</span></strong><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">穿戴甲使用方式</span></strong><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\"></span></strong></span></h2><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">Step1<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">：使用磨甲工具均勻打磨甲面，有助於增加穿戴甲與指甲的接觸面積，進而延長美甲的持久性。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">Step2<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">：利用酒精輕輕擦拭清潔甲面，以去除表面灰塵及油脂。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">Step3<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">：擠出固態膠在穿戴甲上，並以</span>45<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">度角將甲片附著在甲面。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">Step4<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">：按壓甲片約</span>30<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">秒，將其牢固地黏於指甲。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">Step5<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">：照燈</span>2-3<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">分鐘，視乎燈的強弱作調整，便完成</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">固太膠黏貼</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">卸除方式非常簡單，只需使用櫸木棒的斜口端插入於穿戴甲與原生甲的空隙處，噴少許卸甲液並慢慢推移使甲片分開，同時也可將甲片上的殘膠撕掉，以供日後再次重複使用。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; font-weight: bold; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3.</span><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">固態</span></strong><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">果凍膠黏貼</span></strong><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">穿戴甲使用方式跟一般果凍膠使用方法相同</span></strong><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">,<span style=\"font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">但須要照燈。</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:9px\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">固太果凍膠黏貼</span></strong><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">卸除方式跟固態膠方法相同。</span></span></p><h2 style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; color: rgb(128, 0, 0); font-size: 9px;\">#<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">穿戴甲的注意事項</span></span></strong></span></h2><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">1.<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">禁止強力摳除或撕扯甲片，也盡量避免長時間浸泡在水中，防止果凍膠的黏性減弱。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; font-size: 9px;\">2.<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">穿戴甲</span>(</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 9px; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">果凍膠</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; font-size: 9px;\">)<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">能夠維持</span>1<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">至</span>3<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">天的效果，期間若發生鬆動等情況，建議卸除或重新更換新甲片。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;text-indent:10px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; font-size: 9px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">穿戴甲</span>(</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 9px; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">固太膠</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; font-size: 9px;\">)<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">能夠維持</span>10<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">至</span>20<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">天的效果，期間若發生鬆動等情況，建議卸除或重新更換新甲片。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;text-indent:9px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; font-size: 9px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">穿戴甲</span>(</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 9px; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">固太</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 9px; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">果凍膠</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; font-size: 9px;\">)<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">能夠維持</span>10<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">至</span>20<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: MingLiU_HKSCS-ExtB;\">天的效果，期間若發生鬆動等情況，建議卸除或重新更換新甲片。</span></span></span></p><p sty