y: SimSun;\">：使用果冻胶黏贴在指甲，并以</span>45<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: SimSun;\">度角将甲片附着在甲面。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">Step4<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: SimSun;\">：按压甲片约</span>30<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: SimSun;\">秒，将其牢固地黏于指甲后便完成。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-family: SimSun;\">果冻胶黏贴</span></strong><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-family: SimSun;\">卸除方法</span></strong><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-family: SimSun;\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-family: SimSun;\">果冻胶黏贴</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">卸除方式非常简单，只需使用榉木棒的斜口端插入于穿戴甲与原生甲的空隙处，并慢慢推移出果冻胶，同时也可利用木棒将甲片上的残胶卷除，以供日后再次重复使用。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><h2 style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; font-size: 9px;\">2. <span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: SimSun;\">固太胶黏贴</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 11px; font-family: SimSun;\">穿戴甲使用方式</span></strong></span></h2><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">Step1<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: SimSun;\">：使用磨甲工具均匀打磨甲面，有助于增加穿戴甲与指甲的接触面积，进而延长美甲的持久性。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">Step2<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: SimSun;\">：利用酒精轻轻擦拭清洁甲面，以去除表面灰尘及油脂。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">Step3<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: SimSun;\">：挤出固态胶在穿戴甲上，并以</span>45<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: SimSun;\">度角将甲片附着在甲面。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">Step4<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: SimSun;\">：按压甲片约</span>30<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: SimSun;\">秒，将其牢固地黏于指甲。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">Step5<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: SimSun;\">：照灯</span>2-3<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: SimSun;\">分钟，视乎灯的强弱作调整，便完成</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-family: SimSun;\">固太胶黏贴</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">卸除方式非常简单，只需使用榉木棒的斜口端插入于穿戴甲与原生甲的空隙处，喷少许卸甲液并慢慢推移使甲片分开，同时也可将甲片上的残胶撕掉，以供日后再次重复使用。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; font-weight: bold; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3.</span><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: SimSun;\">固态果冻胶黏贴</span></strong><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">穿戴甲使用方式跟一般果冻胶使用方法相同</span>,<span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">但须要照灯。</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: SimSun;\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:9px\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: SimSun;\">固太果冻胶黏贴</span></strong><span style=\"background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: SimSun;\">卸除方式跟固态胶方法相同。</span></span></p><h2 style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; color: rgb(128, 0, 0); font-size: 9px;\">#<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: SimSun;\">穿戴甲的注意事项</span></span></strong></span></h2><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">1.<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: SimSun;\">禁止强力抠除或撕扯甲片，也尽量避免长时间浸泡在水中，防止果冻胶的黏性减弱。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; font-size: 9px;\">2.<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: SimSun;\">穿戴甲</span>(</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 9px; font-family: SimSun;\">果冻胶</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; font-size: 9px;\">)<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: SimSun;\">能够维持</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: SimSun;\">至</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: SimSun;\">天的效果，期间若发生松动等情况，建议卸除或重新更换新甲片。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;text-indent:9px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; font-size: 9px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: SimSun;\">穿戴甲</span>(</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 9px; font-family: SimSun;\">固太胶</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; font-size: 9px;\">)<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: SimSun;\">能够维持</span>10<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: SimSun;\">至</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;;\">20</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: SimSun;\">天的效果，期间若发生松动等情况，建议卸除或重新更换新甲片。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;text-indent:9px;padding:0 0 0 0 ;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;vertical-align:baseline;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; font-size: 9px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: SimSun;\">穿戴甲</span>(</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 9px; font-family: SimSun;\">固太果冻胶</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;; font-size: 9px;\">)<span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: SimSun;\">能够维持</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;;\">10</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: SimSun;\">至</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;;\">20</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: SimSun;\">天的效果，期间若发生松动等情况，建议卸除或重新更换新甲片。</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;tex