2, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lato\">指甲油式刷頭，色彩飽和</span>~<span style=\"font-family:Lato\">適合塗刷底色，容易操作，可快速塗佈，表面容易整平，也可製作造型變化！可卸式凝膠。</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-left: 0;text-indent: 0;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lato\">指甲油式刷頭，色彩飽和</span>~</span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Calibri Light&#39;;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lato\">可當底色塗刷、也可彩繪，不流動的特性還可繪製出</span>2D<span style=\"font-family:Lato\">浮雕造型圖案！</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lato\">容易操作，可快速塗佈，表面容易整平，也可製作造型變化！</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 0;text-indent: 0;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lato\">分類位置：</span>Lorrie gel-<span style=\"font-family:Lato\">凝膠類，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">Gel Nail Product&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\">,</span> </p><p style=\"margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;background:rgb(255,255,255)\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Calibri Light&#39;;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lato\">造型彩膠</span> - </span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 0;text-indent: 0;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Arial Narrow&#39;;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 13px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lato\">操作指引：</span> <span style=\"font-family:Lato\">底膠、色</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;color: rgb(102, 102, 102);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Lato\">膠</span></span><span style=\"font-family: &#39;Arial