(3, 'Coffee Course 01', 'courses', 'Coffee Course 01', '<p>\n	<span style=\"background-color:#FFFAF4;color:#212529;font-family:&quot;PingFang HK&quot;;font-size:28px;\"> </span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	Just like there are people who love languages or beautiful landscapes, there are others who share a passion for coffee. We like to think that anyone can be swayed by the bean\'s calling, which is why we open up our Barista Masters program to anyone who joins as a barista (also known as a partner); even if they don\'t know cappuccino Coffee crema. *\n</p>\n<p>\n	From their first day, partners are guided down a path of tantalizing flavors and textures. We take them on a journey into different growing regions around the world, helping them develop the palate of true connoisseurs from the start. Not only do they learn the basics about coffee and its rich history, but they learn how to make their own and show you this knowledge in-store.\n</p>', '2023-05-15 02:08:50', 'http://dev.coffee.com/uploads/image/20230515/1a89bf8a074d2ca3d9e5c9831c223c26.png', 'https://vjs.zencdn.net/v/oceans.mp4', 1),
