(1, 'en', NULL, NULL, '90826755', '09:30-18:30', '[\"09:00\",\"18:00\"]', 'Mon- Sat', '1,2,3,4,5,6,0,7', 'Room B, 1/F,  2 Ting Fu Street, Ngau Tau Kok, Kwun Tong', '九龍牛頭角定富街2號, 1/F, B室', '九龙牛头角定富街2号, 1/F, B室', '90826755', 'New Beauty Image Creations', '新美纖體美容', '<p>New Beauty Image Creations adheres to the attitude of enthusiasm, challenge and innovation, combines artistic and innovative design with a professional and complete education system, and passes on nail art technology with the spirit of not keeping it private. ESIN products use an absolutely professional perspective in research and development to create the most exquisite nail products. Continuously provide innovative design materials and unique creative inspiration. It is a best-selling brand that is extremely popular among manicurists in Taiwan.<br/><strong>Brand story</strong><br/>1. ESIN products use expertise in research and development to create the most exquisite nail products. Continuously provide innovative design materials and unique creative inspiration. It is a best-selling brand that is extremely popular among manicurists in Taiwan.<br/>2. Moe Gel is a brand of Japanese MIKI GROUP Co., Ltd. It is developed under the supervision of well-known Japanese nail art masters and uses high-quality resin made in Japan as raw materials. The non-allergenic formula is suitable for all kinds of nail types. It has fine texture, excellent leveling and ductility, and good color. Rich and saturated. It is loved by manicurists and is affectionately called &quot;Cute Glue&quot; by people inside and <strong>outside the industry.</strong><br/>3. In the research and development of PRO-D products, we use our expertise to create the most exquisite nail products. Continuously provide innovative design materials and creative inspiration.<br/><strong>Brand spirit</strong><br/>1. ESIN products use expertise in research and development to create the most exquisite nail products. Continuously provide innovative design materials and unique creative inspiration.<br/>2. It is developed under the supervision of a well-known Japanese manicure master and uses high-quality resin made in Japan as raw materials. The non-allergenic formula is suitable for all kinds of nail types. It has a fine texture, excellent leveling and ductility, and rich colors and high saturation.<br/><strong>team member<br/>Tutor qualification</strong><br/>The founder of the company, Daisy Li, is a member of the &quot;Beauty Industry Training Advisory Committee of the Education and Manpower Bureau&quot; and a &quot;Government Qualifications Framework Assessor&quot;. She is also a beauty and manicure instructor for the Employees Training Board and skills improvement. She strongly supports the development of the industry and actively implements related Policies and Measures. The college actively participates in international beauty and manicure industry competitions to allow students to improve their skills. In 2019, she also obtained the gold medal instructor qualification of &quot;Cross-Strait Beauty and Manicure&quot;.</p>', 'https://www.facebook.com/newbeautyhk/', 'https://www.instagram.com/newbeauty_image_creations/', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m16!1m12!1m3!1d3690.9528499319094!2d114.21365387496837!3d22.317622879674193!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!2m1!1z5Lmd6b6N54mb6aCt6KeS5a6a5a-M6KGXMuiZnywgMS9GLCBC5a6k!5e0!3m2!1szh-TW!2stw!4v1723629476869!5m2!1szh-TW!2stw', '', 'beautyforeverme@yahoo.com.hk', '[{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/newbeautyimage.hk\\/uploads\\/image\\/20240706\\/772507eec7a3f2a491d028dd43f4bff8.jpeg\",\"name\":\"PAYME.jpeg\",\"size\":\"146843\"}]', '<p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\"></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\"></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: 微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: auto; margin-bottom: auto; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 細明體; color: rgb(128, 0, 128); font-size: 16px;\"></span></strong>New Beauty Image Creations&nbsp;秉持著熱忱,&nbsp;挑戰創新的態度,&nbsp;將藝術創新的設計結合専業完整教育系統,&nbsp;以不私藏的精神將美甲技術傳承下去。ESIN產品在研發上用場絕對專業角度打造最精緻的美甲產品。不斷提供創新的設計素材,&nbsp;及獨一無二的創作靈感。在台灣是極受美甲師喜愛的暢銷品牌。<br/><strong>品牌故事</strong><br/>1. ESIN產品在研發上用専業打造最精緻的美甲商品。不斷提供創新的設計素材,及獨一無二的創作靈感。在台灣是極受美甲師喜愛的暢銷品牌。<br/>2. Moe Gel為日本株式會社MIKI GROUP旗下品牌，由日本知名美甲大師監製選用日本制優質樹脂為原材料研製而成，無敏配方適用於各種甲質，質地細膩流平性延展性優良，色彩豐富飽和度高。被受美甲師們的喜愛，被業內外人士親切地稱為’萌膠‘<br/>3. PRO-D&nbsp;產品在研發上, 用専業打造最精緻的美甲商品。不斷提供創新的設計素材及創作靈感。<br/><strong>品牌精神</strong><br/>1. ESIN產品在研發上用専業打造最精緻的美甲商品。不斷提供創新的設計素材,及獨一無二的創作靈感。<br/>2.&nbsp;由日本知名美甲大師監製選用日本制優質樹脂為原材料研製而成，無敏配方適用於各種甲質，質地細膩流平性延展性優良，色彩豐富飽和度高。<br/><strong>團隊成員<br/>導師資格</strong><br/>公司創辦人&nbsp;Daisy Li為「教育統籌局美容行業培訓諮詢委員會」及「政府資歷&nbsp;架構評核員」,亦是僱員培訓局和技能提升的美容美甲導師,她大力支持業界發&nbsp;展,並積極推行相關之政策及措施。&nbsp;學院積極參與國際美容美甲行業比賽,讓&nbsp;學員提升技能。2019&nbsp;年更獲得「中華兩岸美容美甲」金牌導師資格。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: auto; margin-bottom: auto; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: auto; margin-bottom: auto; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\"></span></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"text-wrap: nowrap;\"><br/></span></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: auto; margin-bottom: auto; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span><br/></p>', '<p style=\"line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei; font-size: 14px;\">New Beauty Image Creations 秉持着热忱, 挑战创新的态度, 将艺术创新的设计结合専业完整教育系统, 以不私藏的精神将美甲技术传承下去。 ESIN产品在研发上用场绝对专业角度打造最精致的美甲产品。不断提供创新的设计素材, 及独一无二的创作灵感。在台湾是极受美甲师喜爱的畅销品牌。<br/><strong>品牌故事</strong><br/>1. ESIN产品在研发上用専业打造最精致的美甲商品。不断提供创新的设计素材,及独一无二的创作灵感。在台湾是极受美甲师喜爱的畅销品牌。<br/>2. Moe Gel为日本株式会社MIKI GROUP旗下品牌，由日本知名美甲大师监制选用日本制优质树脂为原材料研制而成，无敏配方适用于各种甲质，质地细腻流平性延展性优良，色彩丰富饱和度高。被受美甲师们的喜爱，被业内外人士亲切地称为’萌胶‘<br/>3. PRO-D 产品在研发上, 用専业打造最精致的美甲商品。不断提供创新的设计素材及创作灵感。<br/><strong>品牌精神</strong><br/>1. ESIN产品在研发上用専业打造最精致的美甲商品。不断提供创新的设计素材,及独一无二的创作灵感。<br/>2. 由日本知名美甲大师监制选用日本制优质树脂为原材料研制而成，无敏配方适用于各种甲质，质地细腻流平性延展性优良，色彩丰富饱和度高。<br/><strong>团队成员<br/>导师资格</strong><br/>公司创办人Daisy Li为「教育统筹局美容行业培训咨询委员会」及「政府资历架构评核员」,亦是雇员培训局和技能提升的美容美甲导师,她大力支持业界发展,并积极推行相关之政策及措施。 学院积极参与国际美容美甲行业比赛,让 学员提升技能。 2019 年更获得「中华两岸美容美甲」金牌导师资格。</span></p>', '[{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/newbeautyimage.hk\\/uploads\\/image\\/20240706\\/12781426605ba2885365dab74420f6c9.jpeg\",\"name\":\"ALIPAY.jpeg\",\"size\":\"66487\"}]');
